export default function ServiceArea(){ return(
What we are doing

We Are In A Mission To Help The Helpless

Food

Food donations help people who are hungry and malnourished. They also support local food suppliers. You can donate food in different ways and places.

Book

Book donations are a great way of sharing knowledge and joy with others. You can donate books to libraries, schools, charities or individuals who need them. Book donations can improve literacy, education and culture.

Clothes

Clothes donations give your old clothes a new life. Help someone in need and reduce waste. Donate clothes today and make a difference.

); }
